Khader Adnan: Palestinian hunger striker takes on Israel
Former Palestinian prisoner in Israeli jail, Siham al-Heeh, holds a portrait of Khader Adnan, a Palestinian held in an Israeli prison without trial and who is on hunger strike since December 18, during a protest in front of the Red Cross office in the West Bank city of Hebron on February 20, 2012. AFP PHOTO/HAZEM BADER